ygData.subject: 49th Song Idea
ygData.msgSnippet: Hail All, Why don t we ask for a very simple song for 49? Unvis Undead, nothing fancy, just plain old invis undead. It can t be twisted with anything, subjecst
ygData.messageBody:
Hail All,

Why don't we ask for a very simple song for 49? Unvis Undead, nothing fancy,
just plain old invis undead. It can't be twisted with anything, subjecst to
song range, etc, just like all our songs. I understand (sorta) why our invis
song had this component taken out, but now invis undead is about the only
thing we Can't do.



Lady Brilinnia Ban'Sidhe
Knight Marshall, Order of the Rose
Excalibur, Xegony
